org.apache.flink.runtime.taskmanager

Class TaskSubmissionResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.taskmanager.AbstractTaskResult
      • org.apache.flink.runtime.taskmanager.TaskSubmissionResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IOReadableWritable

    public class TaskSubmissionResult
extends AbstractTaskResult
    A TaskSubmissionResult is used to report the results of a task submission. It contains the ID of the submitted task, a return code and a description. In case of a submission error the description includes an error message.
